&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Minimum 5 years of working experience as a full-stack software engineer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
