&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;You’ve built high reliability or security systems, and understand the importance of code robustness and quality in financial domain&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
