&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Create data tools for analytics and data scientist team members that assist them in building and optimizing our product into an innovative industry leader.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
